#: ../../campaigns/atl01.wmf/scripting/texts.lua:564
msgid ""
"A friend of mine explored the island on his own and he told me of a big "
"lake\n"
"at the top of the mountain. I suggest we build the ships in this lake and "
"wait\n"
"until the island drowns beneath us. Then we can sail away. It is a bold "
"plan,\n"
"but I think, it could work."
msgstr ""
"Un de mes amis a exploré l'île de son propre chef et m'a parlé d'un grand "
"lac \n"
"au sommet de la montagne. Je suggère de construire les navires dans ce lac "
"et d'attendre\n"
"que l'île s'enfonce. Alors nous pourrons repartir. C'est un plan audacieux,\n"
"mais je pense que cela pourrait marcher."

